2025-04-16.title: York VS Staffs (Test Match)
2025-04-16.description:
A 6v6 test match between York and Staffs. This served as a test of the Cheep Cheep app and YouTube streaming.

This match was streamed from both team's perspectives on the UMKL YouTube channel. You can watch those archived streams here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLA9y6mUhnL26e2DXoc9qfiyOymYX5UWHH.

2025-06-13.title: York VS BIMM (Test Match)
2025-06-13.description:
A 6v6 test match between York and BIMM. This match serves to test the Cheep Cheep application and live streaming. Members of the relevant teams can sign up to compete in this match using the button in the team's announcement channel.

This match will be streamed on the UMKL YouTube channel. You can visit it here: https://www.youtube.com/@universitymariokartleague.
